isant un code PIN;\n> Profitez de votre application VROO personnalis\u00e9e : Une interface simple et ergonomique en mode kiosque qui permet \u00e0 vos spectateurs de d\u00e9marrer les films en utilisant leur regard.\n\nPour plus d\u2019informations, contactez notre \u00e9quipe :  hello@diversioncinema.com\n\n\nVROO is a simple solution to showcase 360\u00b0 movies to your audience on Meta Quest devices. Our agency helps you build the perfect VR program for your event!\n> Choose your movies from our catalog. VROO offers more than 30 experiences (Fiction, Documentary, Experimental, Nature & Discovery, Kids, etc.);\n> Launch the application and download your movies using a pin code;\n> Enjoy your personalized VROO app: A simple and ergonomic interface in kiosk mode that allows your spectators to play the movies using their gaze. \nFor more information, contact our team: hello@diversioncinema.com", "short_description": "Pr\u00e9sentez des films 360\u00b0 \u00e0 votre publique en toute simplicit\u00e9 !\nThe easiest way to showcase 360 VR movies to your audience!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://vroo.io/Legal-Notice", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Diversion cinema", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.diversioncinema.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2837265163266059", "context_category": "ENTERTAINMENT"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2777382702530830"}, {"id": "1283811691952063"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED_FOR_DOWNLOAD", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "fr"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SI